INSERT INTO lamport_counter (id, "currentValue", "lastUpdated")
          VALUES (1, 1, now())
          ON CONFLICT (id) DO UPDATE
            SET "currentValue" = lamport_counter."currentValue" + 1, "lastUpdated" = now()
          RETURNING id, "currentValue", "lastUpdated";
